            span.caption.text-muted AngularJS
            img.img-responsive(src='img/angular-ex2.png', alt='')
            p
              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The AngularJS library provides dozens of functions and directives to jumpstart your application. <b><em>Ng-app</em></b> provides module scope, <b><em>ng-init</em></b> to initialize javascript variables, and <b><em>ng-bind</em></b> for evaluating expressions, to name a few. In addition to what comes “out-of-the-box”, Angular’s community has produced numerous third party libraries making problem solving a google search away in most cases.
            h2.section-heading The A In MEAN
