              | &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;People love JavaScript. According to a recent survey of over 26k stackoverflow users, JavaScript has been the most widely used technology since 2014. With the recent development of server and database technologies, it seems safe to assume this popularity will continue to grow, or at least maintain, for the next decade. 
